title: Jewel Quest Curse Of The Emerald Tear [English] [PC]
description: In Jewel Quest Mysteries, Rupert and Emma are plunged into the land of ancient intrigue, Egypt. Seek out treasures and jewels, hidden within stunning gardens and relic-laden palaces. Swap jewels to turn tiles gold in classic Jewel Quest boards, and decipher puzzles of logic and wit. A hidden object game shrouded in the lore of Jewel Quest and the mystique of ancient Egypt. Jewel Quest Mysteries is sure to be the most exciting hidden object game of the year.
